Title: Silk's Silk
Description:
We may not have access to all those fancy plant fibers you surface types use up here, but we do have a lot of options I bet you don't!

The spiders near Loamm make the most interesting smelling silk I ever did sniff. I think it might have something to do with their diet?

If you round some up, I'm sure Rossmar back in Loamm will be happy to teach you a thing or two about how to use it!
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver the supplies to Rossmar in Loamm.
